cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with text detection in natural images. It could also belong to Information Retrieval (cs.IR) as text extraction is a common task in information retrieval. Additionally, it could be categorized under Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with text analysis. Machine Learning (cs.LG) and Multimedia (cs.MM) are also possible sub-categories as the paper utilizes deep learning techniques and works with images.
